@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>PurpleHatProject</h1>

<p>A Blazor Web application with dual database support for both relational and NoSQL data.</p>

<hr />

<h4>Pages</h4>

<ul>
    <li><strong><a href="counter">Counter</a></strong> — A simple interactive counter to verify that real-time server communication is working.</li>
    <li><strong><a href="db-health">SQLite DB Health</a></strong> — Tests connectivity to the relational database with a read/write round-trip.</li>
    <li><strong><a href="dynamodb-health">DynamoDB Health</a></strong> — Tests connectivity to the NoSQL database with a read/write round-trip.</li>
</ul>

